@DATABASE "Jet Pac"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - J - Jet Pac"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - J
                   ====================================

                                  Jet Pac
                                  =======



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(25014,0)"}       25014,0
@{"Lives = x        " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(25367,255)"}       25367,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
